entry.title: Fresh Rescue Efforts Under Way at Ukraine's Azovstal Steel Plant
entry.content: More civilians were being evacuated from the labyrinth of bunkers beneath Mariupol’s Azovstal steel plant as Ukraine’s military counterattacked against Russian forces in the east.

entry.title: Philippines' Duterte Era Ends, Leaving Fate of Tighter China Ties to His Successor
entry.content: The tough-talking populist rocked his country’s alliance with the U.S., forging closer diplomatic and economic ties with China.

entry.title: Mass Graves in Ukraine Reveal Mounting Death Toll
entry.content: Analysis of satellite imagery shows expanding mass burial sites outside of Kyiv and Mariupol.
